fileChanges.details:
Add after the :root block (line 147) and before the .blue block (line 149):

.neon-green {
  --gradient-left: var(--color-neon-green);
  --gradient-right: var(--color-blue);
}

This follows the exact same pattern as the other five color overrides. The color pair (neon-green left, blue right) matches the old hero-specific gradient that was being removed.
